            "id": 6020216,
            "title": "橘焱胡同設職人事業群 象徵高端餐飲文化",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>連鎖餐飲集團橘焱胡同 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2761:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2761\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2761-TW</a>) 不同於上市櫃餐飲同業積極推動每個品牌展店，在內部新設置「職人事業群」，對此，橘焱胡同集團總經理楊哲瑋說明，此事業群不以獲利為主要導向，而是作為跨足高端餐飲市場的象徵。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020216%2Fl%2Fbc05145dceece8310730a3993ba3e9f9.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">橘焱胡同跨高端餐飲。(鉅亨網記者王莞甯攝)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>橘焱胡同職人事業群設有 3 個品牌，包括「天婦羅杉村」、「台北鳥喜」和榮獲 2024 年米其林指南肯定的「鮨中澤」，且並無展店計畫，而是專注展現餐飲集團文化上的差異。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>楊哲瑋指出，具備深厚文化背景、並搭配精緻空間設計的日式職人料理，已成為高端餐飲市場的奢華象徵，而近期最新投資的品牌，是由中澤佑太師傅主理並榮獲 2024 年米其林指南肯定的「鮨中澤」，主打「江戶前板前壽司 × 日本直送食材 × 酒肴文化體驗」，也為集團的餐飲版圖描繪出新樣貌。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>對於集團的起家事業燒肉，橘焱胡同旗下「STAR HUTONG 星胡同」將升級為集團創新 All-Star 旗艦據點，成為未來集團跨界合作、料理研發與體驗升級的領航品牌。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>楊哲瑋表示，星胡同將有更多跨品牌、跨領域的合作陸續登場。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>橘焱胡同以胡同燒肉起家，現今依據不同的市場客群與消費情境，將燒肉類擴張出「星胡同」、「胡同」、「胡同裏」和全新「胡同燒肉酒場」，楊哲瑋認為，燒肉市場群未來營收比重約穩在 30% 左右。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
